title: #191 - Robert Kelly & ME
description: Comedian Robert Kelly & I hang out at the V Cut Smoke Shop & Lounge on Melrose in Los Angeles, have a couple of Tatuaje Cigars & talk about Patrice O'Neal, our problems w/ eating, Tough Crowd w/ Colin Quinn, Opie and Anthony, & the pitfalls of having expectations in show business.
